00:02:56.199 --> 00:02:57.840
umiral sa mundong ito.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:58.800
Ms. Xu,

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:00.520
Ako ay isang doktor.

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:02.719
Siguro hindi ko dapat sabihin ito,

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:03.879
pero ako minsan

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:05.520
